{"tid":960781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國 GPS」北斗三號正式為全球提供衛星定位服務","createTime":"2018-12-29T16:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T03:24:24.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"992bdd4678a7f1df7050797ff299f521bdc4aee2","tid":960781,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2239783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2239783&d=Eo4Nhmzh%2FDEa4pw63Qb4Y%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d40d04fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2239783</a><br />\n提起衛星定位服務，大家可能只會聯想起由美國構建的 GPS（Global Positioning System）。其實衛星定位服務還有歐盟構建的 Galileo、俄國斯構建的 GLONASS 和中國構建的北斗（BeiDou）。當中北斗三號衛星定位系統，最近已宣佈基本系統完成建設，正式開始提供全球定位服務。<br />\n<br />\n為了加快北斗三號系統的建設，中國在 2017 年 11 月至 2018 年 11月期間，發射了 10 枝火箭，將 19 顆衛星送上軌道。北斗三號系統的全球定位精度達 10 米，而亞太地區的精度，更可達 5 米的程度，其精度跟 GPS 的民用訊號相近。北斗三號的全球定位服務可在全球 95% 以上的地區使用，同時北斗三號亦設有其他 3 大衛星定位系統沒有的短報文和位置報告功能，包含導航和通信技術於一身。<br />\n====<br />\n好想比中共瘋狂全球監控！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823b455b2b1980e7d65c63b38ffc10c8d123f615","tid":960781,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"手機可唔可以選擇唔接收支那北斗既衛星?"},{"pid":"c8d215b1eecd6b9aca70bd03ded91a5fff903a55","tid":960781,"uid":51933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T18:51:57.000Z","msg":"no thank you"},{"pid":"9834ddd592291902a8983e5feb1e0230cde88a1a","tid":960781,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"823b455b2b1980e7d65c63b38ffc10c8d123f615","tid":960781,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"手機可唔可以選擇唔接收支那北斗既衛星?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T19:36:46.000Z","msg":"都接收唔到<br />\n<br />\n邊有chip姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2c32ed677049f42cc9b85c99c786fc9b4d8646","tid":960781,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T19:38:50.000Z","msg":"iPhone有GPS、伽利略、GLONASS三種導航晶片。<br />\n<br />\n不過冇北斗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ba30e73e91dfc3c0f64e1de5aa731d419029b7","tid":960781,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T20:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c35393d5bb1f6e8099edd002c81d1f107365afad","tid":960781,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}